    "row": 8,
    "rowsha": "hRUfovEa4cnRjdLtT8JR+7j0j9GPMetA40ACXUMCLhw=",
    "originContent": "Fast parallel directory traversal for Golang.",
    "translatedContent": "Golang을 위한 빠른 병렬 디렉터리 탐색기."
  },
  {
    "row": 9,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 10,
    "rowsha": "bI1qbyC7hcraOoetE4QcuZhd5uH4TpL4dG9FwAT4Evk=",
    "originContent": "Package fastwalk provides a fast parallel version of [`filepath.WalkDir`](https://pkg.go.dev/io/fs#WalkDirFunc)",
    "translatedContent": "fastwalk 패키지는 [`filepath.WalkDir`](https://pkg.go.dev/io/fs#WalkDirFunc)의 빠른 병렬 버전을 제공하며,"
  },
  {
    "row": 11,
    "rowsha": "1nVW5Ty95wwXTtpoPJUbtPLQ9ZkOuDNtAw9//idFvGs=",
    "originContent": "that is \\~2.5x faster on macOS, \\~4x faster on Linux, \\~6x faster on Windows,",
    "translatedContent": "macOS에서는 약 2.5배, Linux에서는 약 4배, Windows에서는 약 6배 더 빠르고,"
  },
  {
    "row": 12,
    "rowsha": "sH93On8m0r+Vg/D6ftwQ8R11Um6nQ9CYfjeno144mUM=",
    "originContent": "allocates 50% less memory, and requires 25% fewer memory allocations.",
    "translatedContent": "메모리 할당은 50% 적으며, 메모리 할당 횟수는 25% 적게 요구합니다."
  },
  {
    "row": 13,
    "rowsha": "5q2X3LNWcpH8jmMOj+dKPVICrACeTF2z/iuVD72Q+jY=",
    "originContent": "Additionally, it is \\~4-5x faster than [godirwalk](https://github.com/karrick/godirwalk)",
    "translatedContent": "또한, OS 전반에 걸쳐 [godirwalk](https://github.com/karrick/godirwalk)보다 약 4-5배 빠릅니다."
  },
  {
    "row": 14,
    "rowsha": "Teay5lkDHLgLc0KUCqLdzUH9HcQDIsMy2YE2KucZrjw=",
    "originContent": "across OSes.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
